  "texts": [
    "Bethge et al. [136] proposed a new method to use the traffic condition, weather, and vehicles' dynamic information to detect drivers' emotions, and VEmotion model was used to detect the emotions and the accuracy reached 71.00%.",
    "Liu et al. [135] used an RNN model to detect the drivers' emotions by using the surrounding objects and vehicles' dynamic information.",
    "The accuracy of the detection reaches 71%.",
    "The number of studies in driving-contextbased emotion detection is limited according to Table 7, and further study in this area is needed with the development of CAVs.",
    "V2X-Based Human Emotion DetectionIntegrating V2X technology into driver emotion detection, a driver can recognize his neighbors' emotional states in real-time by exchanging intelligent on-board data with other intelligent devices in ITS."
  ]
